reviewText: Very good collection! My kid loves to watch it every time I put it on my laptop
Always funny every time you see it. Its nice because it has a lot on it so you can't stop watching it until its over.

The two dvd's I bought were not compatable with my UK dvd player.
We were all looking forward to seeing the fantastic shows, but so let down that we didn't know the dvd's would not work.
This was a great show and I am glad that they put them on DVD.
